{"tid":1839264,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港爆肺炎林鄭懶理 瑞士設宴以點心招待商界領袖","createTime":"2020-01-24T10:43:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T14:14:20.000Z","uid":97944,"like":3,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"bd84e6eba5833f24c98178b68bcab6b6644ad833","tid":1839264,"uid":97944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T10:43:08.000Z","msg":"在中國爆發冠狀病毒肺炎疫症並開始傳入香港之際，香港特首林鄭月娥週四在瑞士舉辦聚會接待了 200 名政商界領袖，提供點心和雞尾酒，向這些政商領袖推銷香港的前途一片光明。 彭博報道直言「這是一個艱難的推銷」。<br />\n<br />\nCarrie Lam hosted 200 business and political leaders for dim sum and cocktails at a Swiss ski resort Thursday to reassure them that Hong Kong&rsquo;s future is bright. It was a tough sell.<br />\n<br />\nThe city&rsquo;s leader told the crowd gathered at the World Economic Forum in Davos that Hong Kong was still open for business, despite paralyzing protests and an economy in recession. She also said that officials back home were working to contain the coronavirus that&rsquo;s killed more than&nbsp;two dozen&nbsp;people in China and infected hundreds of others. Hong Kong has identified two cases.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nIn a room decorated with gold candles and red Chinese lanterns for Lunar New Year, Lam said her government &ldquo;will safeguard Hong Kong&rsquo;s fundamentals, including the rule of law.&rdquo; She was also &ldquo;fully confident of the city&rsquo;s future,&rdquo; according to a readout from her office.<br />\n<br />\nJoining about 30 government officials at the &ldquo;Hong Kong Night&rdquo; in Davos were heads of the city&rsquo;s stock exchange, airport and mass transit train operator. The chairmen of conglomerates&nbsp;Swire Pacific&nbsp;and&nbsp;Far East Consortium International&nbsp;also spoke at the event held in a restaurant overlooking the Alps.<br />\n<br />\nLam&rsquo;s overseas charm offensive had already included a splashy marketing and ad campaign in global media outlets. At Davos, she gave a series of television interviews and also met the prime ministers of Luxembourg, Singapore and the Netherlands, as well as the heads of the&nbsp;International Monetary Fund&nbsp;and&nbsp;Julius Baer Group.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n#cupmedia"},{"pid":"9ce0b3851cef1fc5639f8d2e91ee12abb263d468","tid":1839264,"uid":97944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T10:43:55.000Z","msg":"Source:<a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-01-24/carrie-lam-courts-davos-elites-with-dim-sum-to-sell-hong-kong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2020-01-24%2Fcarrie-lam-courts-davos-elites-with-dim-sum-to-sell-hong-kong&d=3ovy23W4cNvxoMUnqPf77QHlXPv3B7QU%2BsV1%2BUkEKpk%3D&h=d2de9392\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-01-24/carrie-lam-courts-davos-elites-with-dim-sum-to-sell-hong-kong</a>"},{"pid":"3f89912f2f21b821a4b580f62a6064d988d094b4","tid":1839264,"uid":2054,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T10:44:45.000Z","msg":"希望歐洲有癲佬斬撚死個臭閪"},{"pid":"703a271786248ccab057bf1128759a6288981481","tid":1839264,"uid":162008,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T10:45:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要話俾醫護知，無論你地決定係點，市民會支持你地</span></span><br />\n<br />\n原Post<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">大家支唔支持醫護大罷工？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">入黎幫手推十次</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1837575\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1837575</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"5ad6cb7d5dede5aff6c336ccc9031b8122a8a7b1","tid":1839264,"uid":97944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f89912f2f21b821a4b580f62a6064d988d094b4","tid":1839264,"uid":2054,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T10:44:45.000Z","msg":"希望歐洲有癲佬斬撚死個臭閪"},"citedBy":0,